### Implementation order and dependencies

```
Phase 1 (shared config)      — no user-visible change, lowest risk, do first
  ↓
Phase 2 (lists, strikethrough, HR, undo/redo)  — biggest functional gain
  ↓
Phase 3 (mobile scroll toolbar)  — do alongside Phase 2, same CSS file
  ↓
Phase 4 (links + floating link editor)  — standalone, can be done after Phase 2
  ↓
Phase 5 (floating selection toolbar)    — depends on Phase 4 for link button
  ↓
Phase 6 (markdown shortcuts)            — one plugin import, very fast
  ↓
Phase 7 (image paste/drop)              — standalone, can be done any time after Phase 1
  ↓
Phase 8 (code blocks)                   — standalone, part of Phase 2 really (CodeHighlightPlugin install)
  ↓
Phase 9 (toolbar consolidation)         — do last, after everything else is stable
```

